data.description: Priced $60,000 below appraised value! This property has it all! Custom built 4-3-3 with formal dining room. Fresh paint through out! Open concept, wood burning fireplace, granite counter-tops & crown molding. Fourth bedroom could be used as a study. Split bedrooms with Jack and Jill bath. Master bath features large walk in closet, separate vanities, & jetted tub. Other extras include water softener, sprinkler system and oversized garage. Enjoy the beautiful views of your very own pond from the dining room & master bedroom. This is a one owner home. Pride of ownership shows. Lots of wildlife, including ducks, geese, turtle, deer and turkey.  The 2000 sq ft shop has a separate well from the house, R-13 insultation, HVAC, one bedroom and bath. Plenty of room for RV or boat parking. All of this situated on 3.580 acres. No HOA!
